        <TD bgcolor='black' valign='top'><font color='white' face='Verdana' size='2'> Everyone always says get Motte in FP.  This is fine if you are starting at hi level.  I went to QHs and he seemed to spawn every 2 hours (I botched the first kill attempt because I was rebuffing when he came by and tried to pull him without all my spells set).  I ended up fear kiting him.  The think you have to watch for in QH is periodically, on of the guards from the towere walks to the WK zone.  He agroed me from the path when I was up on the cliff (Its amazing how fast guards can climb cliffs).  Also remember that Motte is a Pally and will LoH.  My first attempt, my pet had died and he was almost dead, then he LoHed :( .</P><P>Suetekh<BR>Necromancer of 35 Reanimations</P><P>Edited by - Suetekh on 07/11/2002  13:12:32</font></td>
